{"tid":2290281,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（建設民主濕檔）李卓人：食環署前線政治壓力下不敢即時決定將年宵攤位租予支聯會","createTime":"2020-11-18T01:50:28.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-08T06:35:03.000Z","uid":184679,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"2769cbde04d37fd9f675bcd64d5c87c6baddef4a","tid":2290281,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T01:50:28.000Z","msg":"支聯會主席李卓人在一個電台節目指，相信食環署人員在政治壓力下，不敢下決定，要等上司指示，所以在昨日的年宵攤位競投現場，未有即時簽約落實支聯會投得的年宵濕貨攡位。<br />\n<br />\n對於全國港澳研究會理事田飛龍表示，支聯會屬「顏色革命組織」，違反港區國安法，李卓人表示，有關言論是想震懾及威嚇港人，令港人自行退縮，強調支聯會不會退縮，又認為田飛龍的說法反映內地不是講證據，而是先作拘捕再設想罪名，以「欲加之罪」手法尋找證據，香港亦越來越走向有關做法。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2366744/李卓人食環署前線政治壓力下不敢即時決定將年宵攤位租予支聯會\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2366744%2F%E6%9D%8E%E5%8D%93%E4%BA%BA%E9%A3%9F%E7%92%B0%E7%BD%B2%E5%89%8D%E7%B7%9A%E6%94%BF%E6%B2%BB%E5%A3%93%E5%8A%9B%E4%B8%8B%E4%B8%8D%E6%95%A2%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E6%B1%BA%E5%AE%9A%E5%B0%87%E5%B9%B4%E5%AE%B5%E6%94%A4%E4%BD%8D%E7%A7%9F%E4%BA%88%E6%94%AF%E8%81%AF%E6%9C%83&d=KoeRi8LHiva86SpHjnbz1Ux5KyfgaA76LUEybGJClr4%3D&h=f2b53b6e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2366744/李卓人食環署前線政治壓力下不敢即時決定將年宵攤位租予支聯會</a>"},{"pid":"bd8ae8f26b0846450984c834c493d0a1e60d2c06","tid":2290281,"uid":287422,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T01:53:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"402e021189922b562e161d022fc65cf6a072a585","tid":2290281,"uid":8014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T01:54:29.000Z","msg":"係囉 點估到中共會咁衰<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.g